flowchart LR
  Upload[PDF upload] --> Temp[Temporary bounded extraction]
  Temp --> Smart{Intelligent extraction available?}
  Smart -->|yes| Model[Structured extraction attempt]
  Smart -->|no| Parser[Local parser fallback]
  Model --> Schema{Schema and evidence valid?}
  Schema -->|no| Parser
  Schema -->|yes| Review[Human review]
  Parser --> Review
  Review --> Confirm{Confirm?}
  Confirm -->|yes| Persist[Persist structured data only]
  Confirm -->|no| Discard[Discard preview]
